<c74object name='dk.list2buf' category='' module='dataknot'>
    <digest>Copy a list to a buffer~
</digest>
    <description>Copies the values of a list to a <o>buffer~.</o>
</description>
    <discussion>The <o>dk.list2buf</o> object copies the values of a list to a <o>buffer~.</o><br/>This is a convenient way of transforming data such that it can interface with other Data Knot objects that expect to receive a buffer.<br/>Be aware that if a <o>buffer~</o> of a known size is not received at the input, it will defer the copying, and the copying will occure in the low priority thread.
</discussion>

